{"tid":2508773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公社科新書hard sell國民身份認同：人治不一定全是負面","createTime":"2021-04-29T04:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T10:14:45.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3962edaedc9653dd3edb9894acf7de59374a3bd4","tid":2508773,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pospbg6kssOLgjaOcEVaFubI4Bw=/804x603/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SJY2DHSZBBBTPLRMOVJ36X7TSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fpospbg6kssOLgjaOcEVaFubI4Bw%3D%2F804x603%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSJY2DHSZBBBTPLRMOVJ36X7TSE.jpg&h=107b79f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n書中以補充資料形式，稱「人治不一定全是負面的」。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fzz3M15-8i0Ez7HfzbpKl0L-G-E=/802x443/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UGF33N3LVVFS3EZ2JJWS637QFM.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ffzz3M15-8i0Ez7HfzbpKl0L-G-E%3D%2F802x443%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUGF33N3LVVFS3EZ2JJWS637QFM.PNG&h=f1a85202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n該書「『一國兩制』下的香港」一冊建議教師問及學生看區旗與區徽時有何感受，若感光榮自豪，代表學生本地居民身份認同較高；奏國歌時會感動反映有愛國情懷。另建議教師提問對釣魚台被日本侵佔的感受，若學生感不開心、替國家不值等，反映其國民身份認同。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/TB5WD6FYGNFR7FGUSEYOONG5GI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FTB5WD6FYGNFR7FGUSEYOONG5GI%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=0805a218\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FTB5WD6FYGNFR7FGUSEYOONG5GI%2F&h=27811555\" target=\"_